last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 14
last_episode_to_air.overview: Fantasy dates are here and the girls have one last chance to impress Moses before he makes his biggest decision yet.

name: The Bachelor New Zealand
overview: New Zealand version of the reality dating competition where a single bachelor dates multiple women over several weeks, narrowing them down to hopefully find his true love.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: Get ready for another great Kiwi love story - with all the drama, romance and roses as Soulful Sol3 Mio crooner Moses Mackay starts his very own journey to find the perfect match.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Introducing New Zealand's very first Bachelor, as he embarks on a once-in-a-lifetime quest to find true love with the woman of his dreams. Tonight he will meet 21 very different kiwi women - all with their eyes on the prize.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Love is in the air as one lucky bachelorette flies high on the very first single date, leaving the rest of the girls grounded, and in an action packed group date, true colours begin to emerge.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Love scales new heights when The Bachelor takes one Bachelorette on a date with a difference. The group date spins out of control and a shocking twist changes everything at the rose ceremony.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: The girls get down and dirty in an attempt to grab the Bachelor's attention, but for one Bachelorette the increasing pressure is proving too much, and later, sparks fly as the Bachelor pulls out all the stops in a romantic single date.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Sparks fly when one bachelorette is whisked off on a single date that gets off to a flying start. At the mansion the girls struggle with the new connections that are being made, and passion fails to fire on the group date.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: The Bachelor pulls out all the stops to impress on a spectacular single date. But is he throwing pearls before swine? The group date sees the girls well outside their comfort zone as Mike and The Bachelor put them all through their paces.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: A romantic single date at the Wither Hills winery in Blenheim takes a surprising turn. On the group date things get competitive, as the girls battle it out before an emotional Rose Ceremony turns the competition on its head.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: On tonight's stunning single date, the Bachelor sets sail on superyacht attempting to really get to know his chosen bachelorette, but can she lower her defenses long enough to ensure her safety. Later, tension builds at the cocktail party.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Arthur orchestrates a change of scene for the girls, hoping love will flourish in New Zealand's scenic country side. But when one girl takes a tumble it's not just her safety on The Bachelor that's in jeopardy.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: While one Bachelorette wonders if she will ever get her time to shine, another falls further and further for Arthur's charms. At the cocktail party...a shock announcement turns the competition on its head leaving all the girls wondering - who is going home?

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Arthur whisks a bachelorette off for a romantic date on White Island, but her future on The Bachelor is uncertain after she reveals a deal breaking secret. A surprise serenade makes one girl swoon and panic ensues at the cocktail party.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: On tonight's spectacular date, sparks fly as Arthur soars sky high with one bachelorette. Then a daring double date creates turmoil for the girls and a shock rose ceremony sends a favourite packing.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: With only 4 bachelorettes remaining, it's Arthur's turn in the hot seat. With family interrogations and skeptical friends, can Arthur prove himself to the girls' nearest and dearest.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: With only 4 bachelorettes remaining, Art faces the ultimate test when he meets the last two families on their own home turf. Then in an emotionally charged rose ceremony, one bachelorette will face Arthur for the last time.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: Only 3 bachelorettes remain and Arthur needs more one on one time, so surprises the girls with three overnight dates, but when one bachelorette makes a startling decision Arthur may have to make his toughest choice yet.

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: Arthur's search for love has led him to the final two women, and he is now on the brink of his final choice. To help him with this difficult choice he introduces the final two to his family where one girl makes an astonishing declaration.

episodes.name: After the Final Rose
episodes.overview: In this one hour special, the Bachelorettes talk candidly about life in the mansion. Plus - for the first time, Arthur will come face to face with the women he sent home, before making his first appearance with the girl who stole his heart.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Entering it‘s second season, we meet the next Bachelor NZ and the 23 Kiwi women vying for his heart. And at the ﬁrst rose ceremony, who will get a rose and who will he send home?

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: On the first single and group dates of the season, one girl braves the waves, but will she get a rose for her efforts? And who will go home at the Rose Ceremony?

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Things get messy on when a date at sea turns sticky sweet. Later, puppy love inspires the Bachelorettes competitive side; and a shock exit turns the competition on its head.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: An evening of art and culture leaves one Bachelorette shining, but when a group date gets competitive, shots are fired and boundaries are crossed.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Sol3 Mio's Moses Mackay takes centre stage as he tries to find love. Tonight, Moses meets the girls and takes one on his first single date.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: A single date takes place on the high seas, Meanwhile, back at the mansion, the other women are taking charge of their future with Moses through a tennis tournament.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: At the cocktail party, the girls give one bachelorette a chance to score some crucial one-on-one time with Moses, but will her nerves take over and ruin her chances?

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: The mansion heats up as new arrivals threaten to break existing bonds.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: The drama reaches new heights and there are plenty more surprises in store as Moses continues his journey to find love.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: One bachelorette's relationship status causes confusion and tension amongst the group. Then, a rose ceremony takes place which is bound to turn everything on its head.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: An intruder enjoys a romantic single date with Moses, but this doesn't go down well with the OGs who feel like she should have waited her turn. Then, a group date causes an explosive cocktail party.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: A new day means a new chance to strengthen bonds with Moses. A group date involves a brush with destiny but not everyone likes what the future holds for them.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: A shock departure leaves the bachelorettes feeling unsettled. Two bachelorettes reveal their heart breaking personal stories, and teasing at the mansion goes a bit too far.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Hearts are on the line. A group date raises eyebrows and the cocktail party leaves one bachelorette in the friend zone.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: One bachelorette drops a bombshell, and the others are determined to know if there is more to their connections.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: There are five bachelorettes remaining and tension starts to build as one of them makes a bold move. Later, tears flow as Moses faces the reality of his relationships.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Home visits are on the horizon and with three bachelorettes remaining, who will make the final two?

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Fantasy dates are here and the girls have one last chance to impress Moses before he makes his biggest decision yet.
